  • Field Details

    • guid

      protected java.lang.String guid

      GUID of substitution

      A new substitution is saved if guid is empty on checkin. An existing substitution is updated if a guid is provided.

    • userId

      protected int userId

      The user or group which is substituted by this object.

      This variable is ignored when calling IXServicePortIF.checkinSubstitutions(de.elo.ix.client.ClientInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckinSubstitutionsInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.SubstitutionZ, de.elo.ix.client.LockZ) if userName is set.

    • userName

      protected java.lang.String userName

      The user or group which is substituted by this object.

      userId is ignored if this member is set when calling IXServicePortIF.checkinSubstitutions(de.elo.ix.client.ClientInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckinSubstitutionsInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.SubstitutionZ, de.elo.ix.client.LockZ).

    • substituteId

      protected int substituteId

      User or group to whom the substitution is directed.

      This variable is ignored when calling IXServicePortIF.checkinSubstitutions(de.elo.ix.client.ClientInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckinSubstitutionsInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.SubstitutionZ, de.elo.ix.client.LockZ) if substituteName is set.

    • substituteName

      protected java.lang.String substituteName

      User or group to whom the substitution is directed.

      substituteId is ignored if this member is set when calling IXServicePortIF.checkinSubstitutions(de.elo.ix.client.ClientInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckinSubstitutionsInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.SubstitutionZ, de.elo.ix.client.LockZ).

    • substituteType

      protected int substituteType

      Type of the substitute.

      Read-only, refers to UserInfoC.TYPE_GROUP or UserInfoC.TYPE_USER

    • creatorId

      protected int creatorId

      User who created the Substitution. Read-only.

    • creatorName

      protected java.lang.String creatorName

      User who created the Substitution. Read-only.

    • access

      protected int access
      The current users access rights for this Substitution. Returns a combination of AccessC.LUR_ constants. Read-only.
      Since:
      20.00.000.111

    • groupsToInheritRights

      protected java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> groupsToInheritRights

      List of groups of which the substitute inherits the rights.

      It is not possible to inherit rights from a user, only from groups. Every group needs to have the the right AccessC.FLAG2_CAN_BE_SUBSTITUTED

    • substitutionPeriods

      protected java.util.List<SubstitutionPeriod> substitutionPeriods

      List of time periods in which the substitution is activated automatically if SubstitutionSettings.activatePeriodsAutomatically is set to true.

    • settings

      protected SubstitutionSettings settings
      Contains all boolean settings for a Substitution

    • status

      protected SubstitutionStatus status

      Returns the status of the substitution.

      In case of checking in a substitution, this variable is ignored.

    • forwardedTo

      protected java.lang.String forwardedTo

      If a substitution was forwarded to an other one, this references the guid of the substitution it was forwarded to.

      Read-only.

    • forwardedFrom

      protected java.lang.String forwardedFrom

      If a substitution was forwarded to an other one, this references the guid of the substitution it was forwarded from.

      Read-only.

    • message

      protected java.lang.String message
      Message to add to the substitution.

    • lockId

      protected int lockId

      User ID of the user that has locked the Substitution

      If -1, no lock is held. Read-only, ignored in IXServicePortIF.checkinSubstitutions(de.elo.ix.client.ClientInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckinSubstitutionsInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.SubstitutionZ, de.elo.ix.client.LockZ)

    • lockName

      protected java.lang.String lockName

      Name of the user that has locked the Substitution

      Read-only, ignored in IXServicePortIF.checkinSubstitutions(de.elo.ix.client.ClientInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.CheckinSubstitutionsInfo, de.elo.ix.client.subs.SubstitutionZ, de.elo.ix.client.LockZ)

    • tstamp

      protected java.lang.String tstamp
      Timestamp of last update. Read-only.

    • tstampsync

    • forwardedBy
